{"tid":1867750,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"認清事實，連登唔足以號召人大三罷，香港人未到呢個level，但大型不合作運動仲有啲機","createTime":"2020-02-07T10:03:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-07T10:23:38.000Z","uid":31215,"like":22,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"fe7d790ca3e6327364c4c750c337c443e0766e07","tid":1867750,"uid":31215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T10:03:05.000Z","msg":"今次7000醫護罷工已經係歷史創舉<br />\n之前啲所謂被罷工<br />\n咩612、85<br />\n全部都係被罷工大家心知肚明<br />\n<br />\n而家疫症高鋒<br />\n大型群眾運動黎講<br />\n政黨唔敢號召、民陣唔敢號召<br />\n尤其破壞社會安寧式嘅行動<br />\n燒山講得冇錯，全港最有機會號召到嘅，係得連登仔<br />\n<br />\n但而家啲狗好惡，係又拉唔係又拉<br />\n要勇武又開花<br />\n等如叫手足送頭<br />\n<br />\n唯一轉機<br />\n就係大型不合作運動<br />\n以suck機場、shop爆平安夜嘅規模<br />\n去攻克一啲要點<br />\n<br />\n靠人數唔靠少數人勇武<br />\n分擔責任<br />\n<br />\n2月10又好<br />\n第二日又好<br />\n連登仔唔好9嗌罷工<br />\n太大想頭<br />\n應該精心策劃一次行動<br />\n然後推post<br />\n做好文宣<br />\n同港共玩鋪大<br />\n呢個先係我地能力範圍之內做到嘅事"},{"pid":"c7dc335ca8a0d745bc85627fcc56ea6915f2ff61","tid":1867750,"uid":31215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T10:03:47.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"dc10fae7eea1cd74d41a1255cdf34a9c07944d15","tid":1867750,"uid":31215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T10:04:02.000Z","msg":"721"},{"pid":"57fb0006b8f40d93717810e50793a11860908c76","tid":1867750,"uid":31215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T10:04:12.000Z","msg":"831"},{"pid":"9583d42c38ee6811d6c0a35c73444a0b483f696c","tid":1867750,"uid":31215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T10:04:25.000Z","msg":"101"},{"pid":"a03fc0a1291b7f7c39cc029c6fe76717a2aa6d3e","tid":1867750,"uid":31215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T10:04:44.000Z","msg":"1121"},{"pid":"e87290e612ce9c8bec0eecb5a88b4938705617d6","tid":1867750,"uid":31215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T10:05:04.000Z","msg":"黑警還眼"},{"pid":"e856464a0427923d780b44533333cf1a63622c22","tid":1867750,"uid":312